      "messages": [
        {
          "id": "m1",
          "text": "Did you see the trailers for the new Mandalorian movie? It looks incredible!",
          "senderName": "Me",
          "isIncoming": false,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m2",
          "text": "I did! I'm trying to decide if we should watch it this weekend or wait for the crowds to die down.",
          "senderName": "Wife",
          "isIncoming": true,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m3",
          "text": "Let's go Saturday evening. I already checked the seating chart, and 7 PM still has good spots at the IMAX.",
          "senderName": "Me",
          "isIncoming": false,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m4",
          "text": "IMAX sounds loud, but worth it for the visuals. How much are the tickets?",
          "senderName": "Wife",
          "isIncoming": true,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m5",
          "text": "About $25 each. But we have that gift card from Christmas.",
          "senderName": "Me",
          "isIncoming": false,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m6",
          "text": "Oh right! Okay, let's do it. Book the tickets and send me the confirmation!",
          "senderName": "Wife",
          "isIncoming": true,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m7",
          "text": "Done. See you at home.",
          "senderName": "Me",
          "isIncoming": false,
          "isHighlighted": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "conv_2",
      "title": "Cab Ride with Bucky Barnes",
      "description": "Discussed drop-off location, gate code, and cab fare.",
      "topic_image": "car.fill",
      "notes": "Add notes about this conversation...",
      "participants": [
        {
          "name": "Person 1",
          "summary": "Driver from Brooklyn; requested 120 cash.",
          "image": "avatar_7"
        },
        {
          "name": "Me",
          "summary": "Provided gate code 10042005.",
          "image": "avatar_1"
        }
      ],
      "date": "3 Oct 2025",
      "cal": "2025-10-04T22:30:00Z",
      "start_time": "07:30 PM",
      "end_time": "08:30 PM",
      "category": "friends",
      "icon": "person.3.fill",
      "info": true,
      "messages": [
        {
          "id": "m1",
          "text": "Bucky Barnes, right? How do you spell your surname?",
          "senderName": "Me",
          "isIncoming": false,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m2",
          "text": "B-A-R-N-E-S, Sir. From Brooklyn.",
          "senderName": "Person 1",
          "isIncoming": true,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m3",
          "text": "Nice to meet you, Bucky. Just give me a moment here. I'm looking for the right building.",
          "senderName": "Me",
          "isIncoming": false,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m4",
          "text": "Yeah, I think it is that one over there. The one with the red paint peeling off.",
          "senderName": "Me",
          "isIncoming": false,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m5",
          "text": "You want to dropped here then or near the bus stop? I'm not sure which one is closer.",
          "senderName": "Person 1",
          "isIncoming": true,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m6",
          "text": "The gate would be fine, thanks.",
          "senderName": "Me",
          "isIncoming": false,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m7",
          "text": "What is the code, Sir?",
          "senderName": "Person 1",
          "isIncoming": true,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m8",
          "text": "The code is 10042005.",
          "senderName": "Me",
          "isIncoming": false,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m9",
          "text": "The fare is 120 bucks, Sir. Cash please.",
          "senderName": "Person 1",
          "isIncoming": true,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m10",
          "text": "120! Jesus, the fare has sky-rocketed a lot!",
          "senderName": "Me",
          "isIncoming": false,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m11",
          "text": "I know, Sir. But after inflation, this is the best we can do.",
          "senderName": "Person 1",
          "isIncoming": true,
          "isHighlighted": false
        },
        {
          "id": "m12",
          "text": "Public transport would have been cheaper.",
          "senderName": "Me",
          "isIncoming": false,
          "isHighlighted": false
        }
      ]
    }
