              "text": "That exceeds our forecast. What drove the surge?",
              "senderName": "CFO",
              "isIncoming": false,
              "isHighlighted": false
            },
            {
              "id": "m3",
              "text": "Mainly the new partnership in Singapore. It opened up a lot of doors.",
              "senderName": "CEO",
              "isIncoming": true,
              "isHighlighted": false
            },
            {
              "id": "m4",
              "text": "We should double down on that strategy. Our Q4 focus will be European market penetration.",
              "senderName": "Me",
              "isIncoming": false,
              "isHighlighted": false
            },
            {
              "id": "m5",
              "text": "Agreed. I am allocating an extra $50k to the marketing budget for Europe.",
              "senderName": "CFO",
              "isIncoming": true,
              "isHighlighted": false
            },
            {
              "id": "m6",
              "text": "Make sure the creative team gets the brief by Monday.",
              "senderName": "CEO",
              "isIncoming": true,
              "isHighlighted": false
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
